library(ggplot2)
library(ggnetwork)
library(igraph)
library(sna)
library(intergraph)
  1. igraph
edge_df <- data.frame(
  Source = c("A", "B", "C", "D", "F"),
  Target = c("B", "D", "A", "E", "B")
)
igraph_net <- graph_from_edgelist(as.matrix(edge_df), directed = F)
V(igraph_net)$weight <- 1:5#
## Warning in vattrs[[name]][index] <- value: 
node_count <- length(V(igraph_net))
V(igraph_net)$class <- sample(c("lncRNA","miRNA","gene"), node_count, replace = T)#

new_ggnetwork_net <- ggnetwork(igraph_net, layout = "circle")
ggplot(data = new_ggnetwork_net, aes(x = x, y = y, xend = xend, yend = yend)) +
  geom_edges(colour = "grey50") +
  geom_point(aes(colour = class, size = weight)) +
  geom_nodetext(aes(label = vertex.names),
                fontface = "bold",
                nudge_x = 0.04,
                nudge_y = -0.04)+
